data.description: BEAUTIFUL HOME!! MUST TO SEE!!  3 bedroom 2400 sq ft brick home all on the main level. You  will love the open floor plan and the spacious  size of the family room and dining room with  patio doors that open to the patio both from the dining room and family room to a beautiful landscaped secluded backyard. As you enter the home you will be amazed at the large living room with gas inserted fireplace. The kitchen has plenty of space and is attached to the large dining room. There is plenty of room for entertaining with the extra large family room  with the 2nd gas fireplace.  The two fireplaces with gas inserts  makes this home cozy in the winter. Home has new gas furnace and AC located in the attic. Also it has a new sewer pipe installed from the street. The garage is extra large with a 622 sq, ft  bomb shelter  basement under it.  Great location  close to school, tennis court, and park. This home is a must to see and won't last long.
